<accessionNumber box="[1020,1145,831,852]" httpUri="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/nucleotide/GU989443" pageId="8" pageNumber="731">GU989443</accessionNumber>
. Additional partial COI sequences from 
<typeStatus box="[992,1178,861,883]" isOtherTypeStatus="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="731">other specimens</typeStatus>
collected in the wild in the 
<typeStatus box="[883,932,893,914]" pageId="8" pageNumber="731">type</typeStatus>
locality, named Bird2.4 and Bird3.2, have been deposited in GenBank under accession numbers 
<accessionNumber box="[806,1114,953,975]" isEnumeration="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="731">GU989441 and GU989442</accessionNumber>
, respectively
</materialsCitation>
.
</paragraph>
